{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Introduction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;Equal to P&quot;</strong> (<i>=P</i>) is a puzzle game inspired by <strong>Boolean algebra</strong> and <strong>emoticons</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you need to fill various elements into expressions so that, regardless of the value of the unknowns (represented by letters), the expression always holds true.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Additionally, any block with a golden frame must contain part of an emoticon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However, note that: <strong>the game only has 0s and 1s</strong>! In the world of <strong>Boolean algebra</strong>\u00a0where <strong>1+1=1</strong>, how will you discover the solution through a variety of puzzles?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251840/extras/screenshot_2_4.png?t=1729077009\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>(This is a screenshot during development and does not represent the final quality of the game.)</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dozens of handcrafted levels, from easy to challenging</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New mechanics based on modified Boolean algebra (such as subtraction, division, comparision and more)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pixel art and retro music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">=P</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251840/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729077009","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251840/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729077009","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251840/8b224381df178ee21d93d5b2ffb6747e2c49ec04/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729077009","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste